    <item>
      <title>Catanks</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/projects/catanks/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/projects/catanks/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://store.steampowered.com/app/3793790/Catanks/&#34;&gt;Catanks&lt;/a&gt; is UPGRADE’s 2024–2025 semester project, released on &lt;a href=&#34;https://store.steampowered.com/app/3793790/Catanks/&#34;&gt;Steam&lt;/a&gt; as a top-down arcade tank shooter. As producer and one of 2 lead developers, I worked closely with 10+ programmers and coordinated the game’s asset and production pipelines.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I was responsible for much of the core game design and game mechanics programming during the first stage of planning, before shifting my focus to developing the Classic Mode inspired by Wii Tanks. This included implementing advanced enemy AI and pathfinding systems using state machines and bullet-dodging behaviors to give the players a meaningful challenge.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
